name: Aloha Omakase Club - Worldwide Membership NFT

metadata.name: Aloha Omakase Club - Worldwide Membership NFT
metadata.description: The Aloha Omakase Club offers its members exclusive access to the Omakase dining experience and community. Our goal is to introduce people to the world of Omakase including the delicious food, the talented chefs, and the people you meet when you enjoy this inclusive and social dining experience. The Aloha Omakase Club will be launching in New York, Miami, Los Angeles and Honolulu (we do have Aloha in our name) in September and then we will expand worldwide. Our genesis project is limited to 500 members and offers worldwide access.
